---
import { SITE } from '../../config/site';

const domain = new URL(SITE.url).hostname;
// Privacy Policy Content
---

<section class="pt-12 pb-20 px-6" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:9e1zdx">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:jp2zv3">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:pgdhw1">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="text-sm mb-8" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:z0kw1s">Last Updated: 10/12/2025</p>

    <div class="max-w-none" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:jp2zv2">
      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:9e1zdw">
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:z0kw1t">
          Asianfoodsdaily (“we,” “us,” or “our”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit https://asianfoodsdaily.com/.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:section1">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:title1">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4" style="color: var(--text-muted);" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:jp2zv3">
          <p data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:x7hlo0"><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Voluntarily provided information, such as your name, email address, or comments, when you subscribe to our newsletter, submit a contact form, or engage with blog comments.</p>
          <p data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:x7hlo1"><strong>Automated Data:</strong> Non-personal information (e.g., IP address, browser type, device information) collected via cookies and analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics) to improve user experience.</p>
          <p data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:x7hlo2"><strong>Third-Party Services:</strong> Data from platforms like social media, advertising networks, or email services (e.g., Mailchimp) if you interact with our content through them.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:section2">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:title2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627rf">To deliver content, newsletters, or respond to inquiries.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627rg">To analyze site traffic and user behavior for improvements.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627rh">To comply with legal obligations or protect against misuse.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:section3">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:title3">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:x7hlo3">We use cookies to:</p>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627ri">Enhance site functionality (e.g., saving preferences).</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627rj">Analyze user activity via tools like Google Analytics.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627s5">Deliver targeted ads through services like Google Ads.</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:x7hlo4">You can disable cookies via your browser settings, but this may limit site features.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:section4">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:title4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:x7hlo5">We use third-party platforms that may collect data, including:</p>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627s6">Google Analytics: Tracks site usage.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627s7">Email Marketing Services: Manage newsletters (e.g., Mailchimp).</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627s8">Social Media Plugins: Interactions with platforms like Facebook or Pinterest.</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:x7hlo6">We do not control third-party data practices. Review their policies separately.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:section5">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:title5">5. Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:x7hlo7">We may participate in affiliate marketing programs (e.g., Amazon Associates). Clicking affiliate links may earn us a commission at no extra cost to you. These links do not influence our content.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:section6">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:title6">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:x7hlo8">You may:</p>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627s9">Request access to or deletion of your personal data.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627sa">Opt out of newsletters (via unsubscribe links).</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:6627sb">Disable cookies or tracking.</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:z0kw1s">Contact us at hello@asianfoodsdaily.com to exercise these rights.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:section7">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:title7">7. Data Security</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:z0kw1t">We use industry-standard measures (e.g., SSL encryption) to protect your data. However, no online transmission is 100% secure.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:section8">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:title8">8. Policy Updates</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:z0kw1u">We may update this policy. Changes will be posted here with a revised “Last Updated” date.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:contact">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:contact-title">Contact Us</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:z0kw1v">
          For questions, contact: <a href="mailto:hello@asianfoodsdaily.com" class="underline" data-ps="src/components/legal/PrivacyContent.astro:rwmzc2">hello@asianfoodsdaily.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
